OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FSpeaking publicly for the first time,
OL,8,FGus and Emily Forrester tell ITV News
OL,9,FHealth Correspondent Rebecca Barry
OL,10,Fabout the need for more support and
OL,11,Ffunding into their daughter Leni's
OL,12,Fcondition
OL,14,FTwo-year-old Leni is described as "a
OL,15,Fbundle of energy" - a smiling toddler
OL,16,Fwho loves to make people laugh.
OL,18,FEvery new word she learns and every
OL,19,Fdevelopmental milestone she reaches,
OL,20,Fbrings her family immense joy.
OL,26,@vD@cOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
