FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FBut for her parents those moments are
OL,8,Fcruelly double-edged.
OL,10,FBecause Gus and Emily Forrester know
OL,11,Fin the coming years they could watch
OL,12,Ftheir daughter gradually lose all her
OL,13,Fphysical and cognitive abilities.
OL,15,FLeni has Sanfilippo disease, a rare
OL,16,Fgenetic condition often described as
OL,17,Fchildhood dementia.
OL,19,F"Every parent's worst nightmare"
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FIt has been 5 months since doctors
OL,8,Fdelivered the devastating diagnosis.
OL,10,F"All your dreams for your child's
OL,11,Ffuture are taken away," Emily told ITV
OL,12,FNews.
OL,14,F"To be told that she has this
OL,15,Fcondition, and there is no treatment
OL,16,Fand no cure and no support... it's
OL,17,Fcompletely earth-shattering.
OL,19,F"It is every parent's worst nightmare."
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@WO]vD@AOU{D@AOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FWithout treatment, the disease will
OL,8,Fsteadily damage their daughter's brain
OL,9,Fcells.
OL,11,F"Every day that passes without
OL,12,Ftreatment, this toxic waste is
OL,13,Fbuilding up in our child's body,"
OL,14,FEmily said.
OL,16,F"If we can't get treatment, she will
OL,17,Fsuffer the most awful physical and
OL,18,Fmental decline you can imagine and
OL,19,Fthen die in her early to mid-teens."
OL,21,FWhat is Sanfilippo disease?
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@aO]xD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FSanfilippo disease is caused by an
OL,8,Fenzyme deficiency that prevents the
OL,9,Fbody from breaking down certain
OL,10,Fmolecules.
OL,12,FAs those molecules accumulate, they
OL,13,Fcause progressive damage to the brain.
OL,15,FAlthough children appear healthy in
OL,16,Fearly childhood, the irreversible
OL,17,Fdamage usually begins around the age
OL,18,Fof three. Over time, affected children
OL,19,Fgradually lose the ability to talk,
OL,20,Fwalk, eat and drink.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FThere is currently no cure and no
OL,8,Fapproved treatment available in the UK.
OL,10,FRace against time
OL,12,FA clinical trial for a potential
OL,13,Ftreatment is expected to begin in the
OL,14,FUnited States later this year.
OL,16,FLeni's parents are urging the
OL,17,Fgovernment to help fund the research
OL,18,Fso the trial could also include
OL,19,Fpatients in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FHer mother says early intervention is
OL,8,Fcritical.
OL,10,F"Early treatment is key for these
OL,11,Fchildren. The damage cannot be
OL,12,Freversed once it's done," she said.
OL,14,F"If she has to wait six months, that
OL,15,Fcould mean she can no longer talk. If
OL,16,Fshe waits 12 months, that could mean
OL,17,Fshe loses the ability to walk.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@YO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"It's extremely frustrating because
OL,8,Fthe science is there. The data is
OL,9,Fthere. It's proven to be effective,
OL,10,Fand yet we cannot access it."
OL,12,FA potential gene therapy
OL,14,FProfessor Brian Bigger, based at the
OL,15,FUniversity of Edinburgh, has developed
OL,16,Fa gene therapy approach aimed at
OL,17,Ftackling childhood dementia.
OL,19,FThe method delivers a missing gene
OL,20,Finto patients' blood stem cells.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FBut launching clinical trials requires
OL,8,Fsignificant funding.
OL,10,F"We're racing against time," he said.
OL,11,F"She will start to lose brain cells
OL,12,Fand when that happens we're not going
OL,13,Fto get them back."
OL,15,FHe added that government investment is
OL,16,Fvital.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@\O]sD@AOUuD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"Charities typically can't fund this
OL,8,Fkind of thing," he said. "It would be
OL,9,Freally good if we could see more
OL,10,Fcommitment from government towards
OL,11,Fthese kinds of therapies.
OL,13,F"There are hundreds of kids like Leni
OL,14,Fout there who don't have any therapy,
OL,15,Fand these treatments have the
OL,16,Fpotential to be transformative."
OL,18,FHe claims childhood dementia remains
OL,19,Fan overlooked issue.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@OO]pD@ZOUuD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"All of us have a family member who's
OL,8,Fbeen affected by dementia. Childhood
OL,9,Fdementia is no different. It's just
OL,10,Fmuch, much worse - because it's your
OL,11,Fkid."
OL,13,FCalls for screening and support
OL,15,FChildhood dementia affects around 240
OL,16,Fchildren born in the UK each year.
OL,18,FLeni's parents are calling for newborn
OL,19,Fscreening to help detect rare genetic
OL,20,Fconditions earlier and for more
OL,21,Ffunding to accelerate treatments.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
