OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"As parents, your role is to protect
OL,8,Fyour children and provide every
OL,9,Fopportunity you can," her father Gus
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Without any treatment, her future and
OL,13,Fher reality is very, very dark."
OL,15,FHe argues that rare diseases
OL,16,Fcollectively affect many families.
OL,18,F"When you group all these rare
OL,19,Fconditions together, they suddenly
OL,20,Fdon't become that rare. They affect a
OL,21,Flot of people and a lot of families."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@UO]tD@AOUuD@`O]zD@AOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FFor her mother, it feels like an
OL,8,Funfair battle.
OL,10,F"We shouldn't have to fight for our
OL,11,Fchild's life," Emily said.
OL,13,F"She is as valuable as any other
OL,14,Fchild. But no one is fighting for her."
OL,16,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,17,Fspokesperson said: "Our thoughts are
OL,18,Fwith all those living with dementia
OL,19,Fand rare conditions including
OL,20,FSanfilippo syndrome.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@NO]uD@AOUvD@gO]yD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774335860
OL,3,CParents in 'race against time' to save
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old girl diagnosed with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"We are making sure patients with rare
OL,8,Fdiseases, like Sanfilippo syndrome,
OL,9,Fget a definite diagnosis faster, while
OL,10,Fimproving access to specialist care,
OL,11,Ftreatment and drugs.
OL,13,F"At the same time we are working hard
OL,14,Fto find new ways to slow down the
OL,15,Fprogress of the dementia, speed up
OL,16,Fdiagnosis and improve our
OL,17,Funderstanding of the disease."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
